[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]The Armed Forces Act 2011 
[normal]placed a requirement on the Secretary of State 
[normal]for Defence to make an annual statement to Parliament on the operation of the military covenant. This was the first legislative commitment pertaining to services provided to support service personnel. 
[normal]We have
[normal] undertaken a series of inquiries 
[normal]on the theme o
[normal]f
[normal] 
[normal]The Armed Forces Covenant in action?
[normal], examining military casualties, accommodation, education of 
[normal]S
[normal]ervice personnel and the education of children of 
[normal]S
[normal]ervice personnel. 
